description.en: Eggplant Finance is a DeFi protocol that runs on Binance Smart Chain,  with the goal of delivering innovative yield farming features and token-based gaming/NFT elements.  The Eggplant platform will feature a variety of token based mini games, NFT staking pools and Marketplace, and other crypto portfolio features that aim to bring maximum gains to the customers.
